snippet.title: Style Showdown Saoirse Ronan and Amber Heard Turn Up the Sparkle in Temperley London
snippet.description:
Style Showdown Saoirse Ronan and Amber Heard Turn Up the Sparkle in Temperley London and More Matching Celebs.
The temps may have dropped, but the showdowns are still heating up. With the fall/winter season, we expect to see stars outfitted in looks more in tune with colder weather, so get ready for a lot of layers, crisp jackets and statement boots. While we’re sure they’ll be a few rule breakers in the mix, we’re excited to see which items are so nice, celebs had to wear them twice.
